{"tid":1887081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"灣仔金紫荊男子墮海亡","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:22:35.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d85b115d94d5ac9de11a8055e70d123b65854052","tid":1887081,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERnShAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERnShAR.jpg&h=c5970c36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hROujPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhROujPc.jpg&h=a49d035a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔金紫荊對開，早上9時13分，一名54歲男子被發現在離岸10米海面載浮載沉，保安發現報案，消防船趕至將他救起，他昏迷不醒送院，惟經搶救後證實不治。警方在現場附近撿獲事主的背囊，內有遺書，警方正調查其墮海原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5A8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=869bb792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"bdaff995028df81f234c2f636dfa30a6c5c22cbf","tid":1887081,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌"},{"pid":"61149216d64c5e70efb6fc490a81a3469580dd82","tid":1887081,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1bc43e4d36b668bd598e3be091dec6a22e5c74","tid":1887081,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"調乜查呀，無可疑呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e4b81b1111e2eff2ecd489630d634